autre : l’image de la Chine et de l’Occident. Il propose une réflexion sur les rencontres et les interactions interculturelles entre la Chine et l’Occident dans une perspective interdisciplinaire pour contribuer à l’avancement de la recherche dans ce domaine.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aIntercultural communicationvCongresses. 0aIntercultural communication. 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh  ajésuites, missionnaires.  aéchanges culturels, Chine impériale, dynasties des Ming, Mozi, Occident.1 aAlexeeva, Olga V., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAuger, Réginald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDaniel, Yvan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDéry, Carl, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGhiglione, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJiang, Pei, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJiang, Pei, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aJin, Wan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLandry-Deron, Isabelle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaugrand, Frédéric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLi, Shenwen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLi, Shenwen, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMeng, Qingbo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPang, Naiming, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPinson, Guillaume, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPinson, Guillaume, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPioffet, Marie-Chri